Interface IListActions<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of list elements.
    All Superinterfaces:
    IPerambulateListActions<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MS_StringList

    public interface IListActions<T>
extends IPerambulateListActions<T>
    Interface defines main actions with T type lists.

    1.4.

      • getIndex

        int getIndex(T aItem)
        Returns index of first matching item in the list. If element is not found returns -1.
        Parameters:
        aItem - object of type T which matches one of elements in the list.
        Returns:
        [-1..count-1]

      • edit

        void edit(int aIndex,
          T aNewItem)
        Changes item at index aIndex with passed item aNewItem. Does nothing if index not in bounds.
        Parameters:
        aIndex - index of target item.
        aNewItem - item which will take place of an old item.

        Parameters:

        Returns:
